ion3\" data-albumname=\"\">\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/span>\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/span>\r\n\r\n\t\t\t<span class=\"entry_duration mpfe_fix_lh\"><\/span>\t\t\r\n\r\n\t\t\t<span class=\"song_buy_icons compact_buy_icons transition3 clearfix mobile_visibility_hide\">\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/span>\r\n\r\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\r\n\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\r\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\r\n\t\t\t<\/div>\r\n\t\t<\/div>\r\n\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-5972a84 all-sections-heading elementor-widget elementor-widget-heading\" data-id=\"5972a84\" data-element_type=\"widget\" id=\"section-1\" data-settings=\"{&quot;ekit_we_effect_on&quot;:&quot;none&quot;}\" data-widget_type=\"heading.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<h2 class=\"elementor-heading-title elementor-size-default\">Introduction<\/h2>\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-7b6739c elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor\" data-id=\"7b6739c\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-settings=\"{&quot;ekit_we_effect_on&quot;:&quot;none&quot;}\" data-widget_type=\"text-editor.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<p>Having reliable customer support is like having a good friend you can rely on when using CRM platforms like Salesforce or HubSpot. It\u2019s the helpful hand that guides you when you\u2019re stuck or facing issues. This blog is here to help you compare the customer support of <a href=\"https:\/\/mountainise.com\/blog\/hubspot-vs-salesforce-comparison\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">HubSpot vs Salesforce<\/a>. We will dive into the essence of good customer support and why it\u2019s a crucial part of using CRM systems effectively.<\/p><p>In the upcoming sections, we\u2019re going to look at the help services provided by Salesforce and HubSpot, with some real-life examples to illustrate. By comparing them directly and checking out what users have to say, this blog is here to give you a better understanding of what\u2019s on offer. Your path to making a well-informed choice begins here, as we peel back the layers of support provided by these two well-known platforms.<\/p>\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-980a4f7 all-sections-heading elementor-widget elementor-widget-heading\" data-id=\"980a4f7\" data-element_type=\"widget\" id=\"section-2\" data-settings=\"{&quot;ekit_we_effect_on&quot;:&quot;none&quot;}\" data-widget_type=\"heading.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<h2 class=\"elementor-heading-title elementor-size-default\">Why Customer Support Matters When Choosing a CRM<\/h2>\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-61201f0 elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor\" data-id=\"61201f0\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-settings=\"{&quot;ekit_we_effect_on&quot;:&quot;none&quot;}\" data-widget_type=\"text-editor.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<p>Customer support isn\u2019t just about fixing bugs. In high-stakes <a href=\"https:\/\/mountainise.com\/crm-implementation-enhancements\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">CRM<\/a> usage, support can mean the difference between smooth adoption and costly downtime. When your sales team waits hours for a reply, or your service workflows get blocked, the CRM becomes a bottleneck, not a tool. Good support offers:<\/p><ul><li>Fast, clear responses across channels.<\/li><li>Proactive guidance (best practices, onboarding help).<\/li><li>Stable SLAs for mission-critical issues.<\/li><li>Reliable self-service (knowledge base, community, training).<\/li><\/ul><p>You\u2019ll want a CRM vendor whose support aligns with your business size, budget, and stakes. Let\u2019s see how HubSpot and Salesforce stack up.<\/p>\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-079a7e7 elementor-widget elementor-widget-image\" data-id=\"079a7e7\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-settings=\"{&quot;ekit_we_effect_on&quot;:&quot;none&quot;}\" data-widget_type=\"image.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https:\/\/mountainise.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/elementor\/thumbs\/Good-customer-support-in-Customer-relationship-management-CRM-goes-beyond-just-answering-queries-qwkst3dbm62mqdvp4pk3z54x9zpkc5f3djsjnyni9c.jpg\" title=\"Good customer support in Customer relationship management (CRM) goes beyond just answering queries\" alt=\"Good customer support in Customer relationship management (CRM) goes beyond just answering queries\" loading=\"lazy\" \/>\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-0a27a48 all-sections-heading elementor-widget elementor-widget-heading\" data-id=\"0a27a48\" data-element_type=\"widget\" id=\"section-3\" data-settings=\"{&quot;ekit_we_effect_on&quot;:&quot;none&quot;}\" data-widget_type=\"heading.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<h2 class=\"elementor-heading-title elementor-size-default\">Salesforce Customer Support: What You Get<\/h2>\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-33193c2 elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor\" data-id=\"33193c2\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-settings=\"{&quot;ekit_we_effect_on&quot;:&quot;none&quot;}\" data-widget_type=\"text-editor.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Salesforce\u2019s support ecosystem consists of multiple layers and service\u2010tiers, designed especially for companies that need granular control, SLAs, and robust tools.<\/span><\/p>\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-4ad8b8e elementor-widget elementor-widget-heading\" data-id=\"4ad8b8e\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-settings=\"{&quot;ekit_we_effect_on&quot;:&quot;none&quot;}\" data-widget_type=\"heading.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<h3 class=\"elementor-heading-title elementor-size-default\">Salesforce Success Plans<\/h3>\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-749cd01 elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor\" data-id=\"749cd01\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-settings=\"{&quot;ekit_we_effect_on&quot;:&quot;none&quot;}\" data-widget_type=\"text-editor.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Salesforce offers three main \u201cSuccess Plans\u201d: <\/span><b>Standard<\/b><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">, <\/span><b>Premier<\/b><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">, and <\/span><b>Signature<\/b><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">.<\/span><\/p>\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-98a7d49 elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor\" data-id=\"98a7d49\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-settings=\"{&quot;ekit_we_effect_on&quot;:&quot;none&quot;}\" data-widget_type=\"text-editor.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<table><tbody><tr><td><p><b>Plan<\/b><\/p><\/td><td><p><b>Key Features<\/b><\/p><\/td><td><p><b>Response \/ Availability<\/b><\/p><\/td><td><p><b>Typical Cost \/ Notes<\/b><\/p><\/td><\/tr><tr><td><p><b>Standard<\/b><\/p><\/td><td><p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Documentation, Trailhead learning modules, Knowledge Base, Salesforce Community<\/span><\/p><\/td><td><p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Included with all licenses; self-help\/ community support.<\/span><\/p><\/td><td><p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">\u00a0No extra fee<\/span><\/p><\/td><\/tr><tr><td><p><b>Premier<\/b><\/p><\/td><td><p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Expert guidance &amp; product education; health checks; access to 24\/7 support for \u201cbusiness-stopping issues\u201d<\/span><\/p><\/td><td><p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Faster response times for critical issues; real-time help in some geographies.<\/span><\/p><\/td><td><p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">~30% of net license fees in many cases<\/span><\/p><\/td><\/tr><tr><td><p><b>Signature\u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0<\/b><\/p><\/td><td><p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Designated Customer\u00a0 Success Manager;\u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 proactive monitoring; fastest response times; custom guidance on key events<\/span><\/p><\/td><td><p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Premium availability; highest SLA guarantees.<\/span><\/p><\/td><td><p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Contact sales; significantly higher investment<\/span><\/p><\/td><\/tr><\/tbody><\/table>\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-ef1989a elementor-widget elementor-widget-heading\" data-id=\"ef1989a\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-settings=\"{&quot;ekit_we_effect_on&quot;:&quot;none&quot;}\" data-widget_type=\"heading.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<h3 class=\"elementor-heading-title elementor-size-default\">Other Support Capabilities<\/h3>\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-2c5ce36 elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor\" data-id=\"2c5ce36\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-settings=\"{&quot;ekit_we_effect_on&quot;:&quot;none&quot;}\" data-widget_type=\"text-editor.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<ul><li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\"><b>Self-Service &amp; Training:<\/b><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\"> Large library of documentation; Trailhead (Salesforce\u2019s free training platform) is widely used for onboarding and learning.<\/span><\/li><li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\"><b>Community &amp; Forums:<\/b><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\"> The Salesforce Trailblazer Community is active, rich in peer support.<\/span><\/li><li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\"><b>24\/7 Coverage:<\/b><span> For critical issues, higher-tier customers (Premier &amp; Signature) get 24\/7 support. Standard tiers are more limited.<\/span><\/span><\/li><\/ul>\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-73b7c76 all-sections-heading elementor-widget elementor-widget-heading\" data-id=\"73b7c76\" data-element_type=\"widget\" id=\"section-4\" data-settings=\"{&quot;ekit_we_effect_on&quot;:&quot;none&quot;}\" data-widget_type=\"heading.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<h2 class=\"elementor-heading-title elementor-size-default\">HubSpot Customer Support: What You Get<\/h2>\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-a86431e elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor\" data-id=\"a86431e\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-settings=\"{&quot;ekit_we_effect_on&quot;:&quot;none&quot;}\" data-widget_type=\"text-editor.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\"><a href=\"https:\/\/mountainise.com\/hubspot\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">HubSpot CRM<\/a> support is often praised for being friendly, intuitive, and particularly strong for SMBs and teams with less technical bandwidth.<\/span><\/p>\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-c0f2b83 all-sections-heading elementor-widget elementor-widget-heading\" data-id=\"c0f2b83\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-settings=\"{&quot;ekit_we_effect_on&quot;:&quot;none&quot;}\" data-widget_type=\"heading.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<h3 class=\"elementor-heading-title elementor-size-default\">Support Channels &amp; Tiers<\/h3>\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-c4829b5 elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor\" data-id=\"c4829b5\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-settings=\"{&quot;ekit_we_effect_on&quot;:&quot;none&quot;}\" data-widget_type=\"text-editor.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<ul><li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\">Free &amp; Basic Tiers:<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\"> Access to HubSpot\u2019s Knowledge Base, Academy courses, community forums. Ideal for learning, self-help, small issues.<\/span><\/li><li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\">Professional &amp; Enterprise Tiers:<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\"> Includes live chat, email support, and phone support (depending on region), plus more hands-on assistance.<\/span><\/li><li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Training &amp; onboarding help via HubSpot Academy is frequently cited as a strength.<\/span><\/li><li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Proactive support (recommendations, best practices) tends to be better in higher plans.<\/span><\/li><\/ul>\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-8c0361f all-sections-heading elementor-widget elementor-widget-heading\" data-id=\"8c0361f\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-settings=\"{&quot;ekit_we_effect_on&quot;:&quot;none&quot;}\" data-widget_type=\"heading.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<h3 class=\"elementor-heading-title elementor-size-default\">Real-World Feedback<\/h3>\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-29a1ee5 elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor\" data-id=\"29a1ee5\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-settings=\"{&quot;ekit_we_effect_on&quot;:&quot;none&quot;}\" data-widget_type=\"text-editor.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<ul><li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">According to <\/span><b>Gartner Peer Insights<\/b><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">, HubSpot has about <\/span><b>4.4\/5 stars<\/b><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\"> from ~2,100+ reviews, while Salesforce has ~<\/span><b>4.2\/5<\/b><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\"> from ~660+ in relevant CRM \/ <a href=\"https:\/\/mountainise.com\/marketing-automation\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">marketing automation<\/a> comparisons.<\/span><p>\u00a0<\/p><\/li><li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Users often say HubSpot\u2019s support is \u201cfriendlier\u201d and more \u201caccessible\u201d especially in lower\/mid tiers; Salesforce users highlight greater depth, especially for complex setups or enterprises.<\/span><\/li><\/ul>\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-9be25f9 elementor-widget elementor-widget-image\" data-id=\"9be25f9\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-settings=\"{&quot;ekit_we_effect_on&quot;:&quot;none&quot;}\" data-widget_type=\"image.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https:\/\/mountainise.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/elementor\/thumbs\/User-Testimonials-and-Reviews-qwkstumn4d3y32s3pjcahg9ai5z7jdfb5apmkzj38w.jpg\" title=\"User Testimonials and Reviews\" alt=\"User Testimonials and Reviews\" loading=\"lazy\" \/>\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-41b5fc8 all-sections-heading elementor-widget elementor-widget-heading\" data-id=\"41b5fc8\" data-element_type=\"widget\" id=\"section-5\" data-settings=\"{&quot;ekit_we_effect_on&quot;:&quot;none&quot;}\" data-widget_type=\"heading.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<h2 class=\"elementor-heading-title elementor-size-default\">HubSpot vs Salesforce: Head-to-Head Comparison<\/h2>\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-a6a0d59 elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor\" data-id=\"a6a0d59\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-settings=\"{&quot;ekit_we_effect_on&quot;:&quot;none&quot;}\" data-widget_type=\"text-editor.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<table><tbody><tr><td><p><b>Feature<\/b><\/p><\/td><td><p><b>HubSpot<\/b><\/p><\/td><td><p><b>Salesforce<\/b><\/p><\/td><\/tr><tr><td><p><b>Support Channels<\/b><\/p><\/td><td><p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Chat, email, phone (in higher tiers) + knowledge base, Academy, forums<\/span><\/p><\/td><td><p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Phone, email, online cases + Knowledge Base, Trailhead, Community; more premium support with dedicated CSMs<\/span><\/p><\/td><\/tr><tr><td><p><b>Onboarding &amp; Proactive Guidance<\/b><\/p><\/td><td><p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Strong with Academy &amp; training, less hands-on in lower tiers<\/span><\/p><\/td><td><p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Stronger in premier\/signature tiers, with health checks &amp; success planning<\/span><\/p><\/td><\/tr><tr><td><p><b>Response Time for Critical Issues<\/b><\/p><\/td><td><p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Good, especially for Enterprise plans; live chat often quicker<\/span><\/p><\/td><td><p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Best response times in higher support levels; 24\/7 in Premier &amp; Signature plans<\/span><\/p><\/td><\/tr><tr><td><p><b>Self-Service &amp; Learning Resources<\/b><\/p><\/td><td><p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Excellent; HubSpot Academy and Knowledge Base are highly rated<\/span><\/p><\/td><td><p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Very good; Trailhead training is extensive and comprehensive<\/span><\/p><\/td><\/tr><tr><td><p><b>Cost &amp; Value<\/b><\/p><\/td><td><p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Lower entry costs; more inclusive features earlier<\/span><\/p><\/td><td><p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Higher costs in premium tiers; better suited for large enterprises or complex needs<\/span><\/p><\/td><\/tr><tr><td><p><b>User Satisfaction &amp; Ratings<\/b><\/p><\/td><td><p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Slight edge for ease-of-use, friendliness; good satisfaction scores overall<\/span><\/p><\/td><td><p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Strong for customization, support depth; enterprise clients tend to favor Salesforce for large scale<\/span><\/p><\/td><\/tr><\/tbody><\/table>\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-25bb85a all-sections-heading elementor-widget elementor-widget-heading\" data-id=\"25bb85a\" data-element_type=\"widget\" id=\"section-6\" data-settings=\"{&quot;ekit_we_effect_on&quot;:&quot;none&quot;}\" data-widget_type=\"heading.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<h2 class=\"elementor-heading-title elementor-size-default\">Pricing, SLAs &amp; Hidden Costs<\/h2>\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-a9f2609 elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor\" data-id=\"a9f2609\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-settings=\"{&quot;ekit_we_effect_on&quot;:&quot;none&quot;}\" data-widget_type=\"text-editor.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<ul><li><strong>Salesforce:<\/strong> Premier Success Plan is typically about 30% of net license fees in many scenarios. Signature plan costs vary, but expect significantly higher investment.<\/li><li><strong>Support fees<\/strong> often scale with complexity, custom integrations, high user count, or international support add to cost and implementation effort.<\/li><li><strong>HubSpot:<\/strong> The cost difference between tiers matters. Lower tiers may have limited live-phone support or slower response times; higher tiers reduce constraints and improve turnaround. Also, onboarding or consulting costs (if you work with an agency) may factor in.<\/li><li><strong>Service Level Agreements (SLAs):<\/strong> <a href=\"https:\/\/mountainise.com\/salesforce\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">Salesforce CRM<\/a> offers faster guaranteed response\/resolution in higher Success Plans. HubSpot CRM may offer less formal SLAs; response time often depends on plan and location.<\/li><\/ul>\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-61de08d all-sections-heading elementor-widget elementor-widget-heading\" data-id=\"61de08d\" data-element_type=\"widget\" id=\"section-7\" data-settings=\"{&quot;ekit_we_effect_on&quot;:&quot;none&quot;}\" data-widget_type=\"heading.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<h2 class=\"elementor-heading-title elementor-size-default\">What Real Users Say (Pros &amp; Cons)<\/h2>\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-8b61de8 elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor\" data-id=\"8b61de8\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-settings=\"{&quot;ekit_we_effect_on&quot;:&quot;none&quot;}\" data-widget_type=\"text-editor.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<p><b>HubSpot Pros:<\/b><\/p><ul><li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Excellent self-service training (Academy) and helpful documentation.<\/span><\/li><li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Usability and ease of learning are frequently highlighted.<\/span><\/li><li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Friendly customer service reps, especially in mid-tiers.<\/span><\/li><\/ul><p><b>HubSpot Cons:<\/b><\/p><ul><li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Live support channels (phone\/chat) not always available in lower tiers or in all geographies.<\/span><\/li><li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Response time for complex issues or customization can lag behind more enterprise-grade support.<\/span><\/li><\/ul><p><b>Salesforce Pros:<\/b><\/p><ul><li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Very strong for enterprises requiring dedicated support, custom SLAs, and large-scale operations.<\/span><\/li><li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Richer options for escalation, dedicated Customer Success Managers (CSMs).<\/span><\/li><li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Depth of support for integrations, custom code, business continuity.<\/span><\/li><\/ul><p><b>Salesforce Cons:<\/b><\/p><ul><li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Cost can escalate quickly with add-ons, premium support tiers, or complex customizations.<\/span><\/li><li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">The learning curve is steeper; some support content assumes more technical or administrative resources.<\/span><\/li><\/ul>\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-0994b9c all-sections-heading elementor-widget elementor-widget-heading\" data-id=\"0994b9c\" data-element_type=\"widget\" id=\"section-8\" data-settings=\"{&quot;ekit_we_effect_on&quot;:&quot;none&quot;}\" data-widget_type=\"heading.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<h2 class=\"elementor-heading-title elementor-size-default\">Who Should Pick Which Support Model<\/h2>\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-1189f72 elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor\" data-id=\"1189f72\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-settings=\"{&quot;ekit_we_effect_on&quot;:&quot;none&quot;}\" data-widget_type=\"text-editor.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<p><b>Choose HubSpot if<\/b><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">:<\/span><\/p><ul><li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">You\u2019re a small or mid-sized business wanting fast results with minimal setup overhead.<\/span><\/li><li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">You prefer easy onboarding, lots of documentation, and a support system that feels user-friendly.<\/span><\/li><li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Your support needs are moderate; you don\u2019t require deep technical support or heavy custom code right away.<\/span><\/li><\/ul><p><b>Choose Salesforce if<\/b><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">:<\/span><\/p><ul><li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">You run a large enterprise, with complex workflows, integrations, or global operations.<\/span><\/li><li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">You need firm SLAs, dedicated support (CSM), and higher availability (24\/7 for critical issues).<\/span><\/li><li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">You expect to scale significantly and require granular control over every feature or customization.<\/span><\/li><\/ul>\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-add8cd6 all-sections-heading elementor-widget elementor-widget-heading\" data-id=\"add8cd6\" data-element_type=\"widget\" id=\"section-9\" data-settings=\"{&quot;ekit_we_effect_on&quot;:&quot;none&quot;}\" data-widget_type=\"heading.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<h2 class=\"elementor-heading-title elementor-size-default\">Final Thoughts<\/h2>\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-d4f570d elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor\" data-id=\"d4f570d\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-settings=\"{&quot;ekit_we_effect_on&quot;:&quot;none&quot;}\" data-widget_type=\"text-editor.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Both HubSpot and Salesforce shine in different areas of customer support. HubSpot tends to win in friendliness, ease of use, and inclusive training resources, particularly important if you want fast adoption. Salesforce excels when it comes to depth, resilience, and high-stake support for enterprise or complex use cases.<\/span><\/p><p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">At <a href=\"https:\/\/mountainise.com\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">Mountainise<\/a>, we help companies assess which platform\u2019s support model fits their long-term strategy, so you don\u2019t pay for features you don\u2019t need or end up frustrated with slow responses. If you\u2019d like a tailored comparison for your business (e.g. with estimations for your team size, location, tech stack), <\/span><a href=\"https:\/\/mountainise.com\/book-a-free-session\/\"><b>book a free discovery consultation with us<\/b><\/a><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">.<\/span><\/p>\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-column elementor-col-33 elementor-top-column elementor-element elementor-element-cbe28b0\" data-id=\"cbe28b0\" data-element_type=\"column\">\n\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-wrap elementor-element-populated\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<section class=\"elementor-section elementor-inner-section elementor-element elementor-element-32fe1c4 elementor-section-boxed elementor-section-height-default elementor-section-height-default\" data-id=\"32fe1c4\" data-element_type=\"section\" data-settings=\"{&quot;sticky&quot;:&quot;top&quot;,&quot;sticky_on&quot;:[&quot;desktop&quot;],&quot;sticky_parent&quot;:&quot;yes&quot;,&quot;ekit_has_onepagescroll_dot&quot;:&quot;yes&quot;,&quot;sticky_offset&quot;:0,&quot;sticky_effects_offset&quot;:0,&quot;sticky_anchor_link_offset&quot;:0}\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-container elementor-column-gap-no\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-column elementor-col-100 elementor-inner-column elementor-element elementor-element-e93e9e2\" data-id=\"e93e9e2\" data-element_type=\"column\">\n\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-wrap elementor-element-populated\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-cda30e2 elementor-widget elementor-widget-heading\" data-id=\"cda30e2\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-settings=\"{&quot;ekit_we_effect_on&quot;:&quot;none&quot;}\" data-widget_type=\"heading.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-heading-title elementor-size-default\">Latest WhitePaper<\/div>\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-e0f6eb8 elementor-grid-1 elementor-grid-tablet-2 elementor-grid-mobile-1 elementor-posts--thumbnail-top elementor-posts__hover-gradient elementor-widget elementor-widget-posts\" data-id=\"e0f6eb8\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-settings=\"{&quot;cards_columns&quot;:&quot;1&quot;,&quot;cards_row_gap&quot;:{&quot;unit&quot;:&quot;px&quot;,&quot;size&quot;:5,&quot;sizes&quot;:[]},&quot;cards_columns_tablet&quot;:&quot;2&quot;,&quot;cards_columns_mobile&quot;:&quot;1&quot;,&quot;cards_row_gap_tablet&quot;:{&quot;unit&quot;:&quot;px&quot;,&quot;size&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;sizes&quot;:[]},&quot;cards_row_gap_mobile&quot;:{&quot;unit&